    "content": "<p>$\\mathbf{Assertion (A)}$ Silicones are used for water proofing of fabrics.</p>\n<p>$\\mathbf{Reason (R)}$ The repeating unit in silicones is</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/fly/@width/image/jaoe38c1m5wm0np9/153f914d-5853-4f27-b7bb-a83f9f5604c3/ac6caad0-d289-11ef-acf1-4d81512d7f21/file-jaoe38c1m5wm0npa.png?format=png\" data-orsrc=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/image/jaoe38c1m5wm0np9/153f914d-5853-4f27-b7bb-a83f9f5604c3/ac6caad0-d289-11ef-acf1-4d81512d7f21/file-jaoe38c1m5wm0npa.png\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"max-width:100%;height:auto;display:block;margin:0 auto;max-height:40vh;vertical-align:baseline\" alt=\"TG EAPCET 2024 (Online) 10th May Morning Shift Chemistry - Polymers Question 17 English\"></p>\n<p>The correct answer is</p>",
    "options": [
      {
